name: Tour EP TOTE BAG+CD
description:
Limited to just 20, this is a three track CD inside a specially-printed MC iPod tote bag.

These were made for the September 2012 tour, and any leftovers will be available here afterwards.

The tracklisting is a secret! All I'm saying is it is three cover versions...

name: Assorted KEYRINGS
description: MC iPod keyrings, available in six designs. Full colour design (double sided) in plastic shell.

name: The Avril LIVEigne EP TAPE
description:
Ultra DIY, "bootleg" style, cassette of a live four-song set of Avril Lavigne covers, backed with a full band. Limited to just 10 with hand-stamped sleeves. Comes with a free download.

SIDE A:
01) Sk8er Boi
02) Complicated

SIDE B:
01) I'm With You
02) Girlfriend
